org.jivesoftware.smackx.jingleold.nat

Class TransportNegotiator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jivesoftware.smackx.jingleold.JingleNegotiator
      • org.jivesoftware.smackx.jingleold.nat.TransportNegotiator
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TransportNegotiator.Ice, TransportNegotiator.RawUdp

    public abstract class TransportNegotiator
extends JingleNegotiator
    Transport negotiator.

    This class is responsible for managing the transport negotiation process, handling all the stanza(/packet) interchange and the stage control.
